===Protologisms ending in ''-feminate''===
Female equivalents of words like '''triumvirate''' and '''quadrumvirate''' are protologisms.  The suffix ''-virate'' would become ''-feminate''.  For example, '''triumfeminate''' would be the female equivalent of '''triumvirate'''.

